CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 31, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Glamour! Glamour! - A smooth quartet of Trendette models smile prettily for Teenie Harris, the photographer. Clockwise: Mrs. Joan Hall, Mrs. Nadine Primas, Miss Tanis Armes and Miss Jocelyn Brenson."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Trendettes members; left to right: Joan Hall, Nadine Primas, Tanis Armes, Jocelyn Brenson, and unknown woman, modeling clothing for fashion show at Carnegie Music Hall
